# Build & Release

## 版本

| 产品 | 真相源 |
|------|--------|
| MimicClient (PC) | `pc/client/src/version.h` → `APP_VERSION` |
| MimicServer | `server/package.json` → `version` |
| Mimic Android | `android/package.json` + `android/version.json` |

## 构建

```powershell
cd shared\web; npm run build
powershell -File scripts\Build.ps1
powershell -File scripts\Build.ps1 -Module mimic_client
```

输出：`pc/client/build/{bin,frontend,config}`（exe = `mimic_client.exe`）。

## 一键发布

```powershell
# bump version.h 和/或 server/package.json / android 后:
powershell -File scripts\Release.ps1              # → CDN（默认不传 Gitee Setup）
powershell -File scripts\Release.ps1 -ClientOnly  # PC + Android CDN
powershell -File scripts\Release.ps1 -ServerOnly
powershell -File scripts\Release.ps1 -DryRun
powershell -File scripts\Release.ps1 -PublishGitee  # 可选：薄 Setup 挂 Gitee
```

默认路径：CDN 货架 + 旧 Setup 应用内更新。Gitee Setup 附件需显式 `-PublishGitee`。

Android APK：`Build-Android.ps1` → CDN `http://47.107.43.5/mimic/android/`；详见 `android/README.md`。

CDN：`scripts/Publish-Cdn.ps1`（`-ClientOnly` 含 android）。
